snippet.title: NWO Wars - Trailer
snippet.description:
A classic arcade shooter in which you save the world from the evil globalist plot to turn everyone into bug-eating pod-dwelling libtards! Stay tuned for future bonus levels and characters...

SVGS is the leading free-speech-inspired game development studio, ready to create monumental games for influential figures who tackle serious worldly issues. SVGS battles against the fear of cancel culture, putting privacy first and refusing to deplatform legal content.

Video enhanced from 1080p to 2160p.

https://spawn.video
